ISLAMABAD, May 9 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan Saturday expressed his condolence to Senator Faisal Javed on the death of his mother.
According to a press release of the PM office media wing, the prime minister, in a telephonic call to senator Faisal Javed, prayed for the high ranks of the departed soul.
